ent-WiredApronBase-name = wired apron
ent-WiredApronBase-desc = An apron threaded with cabling. It looks incomplete.

ent-SteelApronBase-name = steel-covered apron
ent-SteelApronBase-desc = An apron with steel plating haphazardly affixed by spare cabling. In it's current state, it would fall apart immediately if worn.

ent-WeldedSteelApronBase-name = welded steel apron
ent-WeldedSteelApronBase-desc = An apron affixed with welded steel plating attached to spare cabling. The armor is no longer in danger of falling apart, but requires additional work to be worn securely.

ent-ClothingOuterArmorScrap-name = scrap armor
ent-ClothingOuterArmorScrap-desc = A tider's gleaming plate mail. Bail up, or you're a dead man.

